   - Go to **Products** and click on the product you want to update
   - Go to the **"Ingredients"** tab
   - Add all the ingredients used in the product

3. **Add packaging**: Ensure your product has all its packaging components added.
   - Go to **Products** and click on the product
   - Go to the **"Packaging"** tab
   - Add all packaging materials used for the product

4. **Calculate the LCA**: Once ingredients and packaging are added, you can calculate the LCA.
   - Go to **Products** and click on the product
   - Go to the **"LCA"** tab
   - Click **"Calculate LCA"**

