	('4fc27ac2-b91e-4a4a-80dc-e06e1bb03806', NULL, 'definition', 'GHG Protocol Scope Definitions', 'Scope 1: Direct GHG emissions from sources owned or controlled by the company (e.g., company vehicles, on-site fuel combustion).
