Scope 3: All other indirect GHG emissions in the value chain, categorised into 15 categories covering upstream and downstream activities.
The platform tracks Categories 1-8 which are most relevant to manufacturing and consumer goods companies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, '{}', true, 90, '2026-01-14 04:05:05.949447+00', '2026-01-14 04:05:05.949447+00'),
