 doing to revolutionise period care. Visit Website LOVEHERO Showing that you care about the planet has never looked so stylish. You can sometimes see Steph looking absolutely fabulous in her LOVEHERO outfits. Visit Website Ben & Jerry''s We all need a little bit of ice cream in our lives, and Ben & Jerry''s are a rare thing: a global brand that really does care and is using their business to do good in the world. Visit Website Neem London Stylish menswear that uses a fraction of the resources to make their products than their competitors. How many bananas does it take to make a Neem shirt? Visit Website Telmont Champagne Who doesn''t love champagne? Telmont are doing the work to reduce the impact of the world''s favourite sparkling wine. They''re doing so many good things even Leonardo di Caprio invested. Visit Website Citizens of Soil Olive oil done right. Single estate, ethical, transparent, organic, and celebrating the farmers that mak', 'medium', 55, 'Avallen makes several strong environmental claims, particularly around being ''climate positive''. While they provide some substantiation, the claims require careful scrutiny to ensure they are not misleading, especially concerning the scope and limitations of their positive impact. The use of generic terms like ''sustainable'' also needs to be backed by specific, verifiable actions.', '["Provide more detailed and easily accessible data on the lifecycle assessment (LCA) that supports the ''climate positive'' claim.", "Avoid generic terms like ''sustainable'' without specific, measurable, and time-bound commitments.", "Clearly define the scope and boundaries of the ''climate positive'' claim, including what emissions are included and excluded.", "Ensure that any comparative claims against industry averages are based on robust and up-to-date data.", "Regularly update and audit environmental claims to ensure continued accuracy and compliance with evolving regulations."]', '[{"name": "Green Claims Code (CMA, 2021)", "j