	('37afb7df-6d7a-4523-9152-06912636677f', '7beb0b16-6492-4e5e-82ba-321d10b780dd', 'Our packaging is made from recycled materials and is fully biodegradable.', 'Description of packaging.', 'medium', 55, 'unsubstantiated', 'While using recycled materials is positive, the claim ''fully biodegradable'' requires substantiation. It needs to specify the conditions under which the packaging will biodegrade (e.g., industrial composting) and provide evidence to support this claim. Without this, it could be misleading if consumers assume it will biodegrade in any environment.', 'Green Claims Code', 'Principle 6: Claims must be substantiated', 'uk', 'Specify the percentage of recycled content and the conditions required for biodegradation (e.g., ''industrially compostable according to EN 13432''). Provide evidence of certification or testing to support the biodegradability claim.', 'Our packaging is made from [X]% recycled materials and is industrially compostable according to EN 13432.', 2, '2026-01-29 15:04:45.819044+00'),
	('79654c8c-f25e-4dee-bde3-7d1f1913c37c', '7beb0b16-6492-4e5e-82ba-321d10b780dd', 'We have reduced our carbon footprint by 50% since 2020.', 'Statement of carbon footprint reduction.', 'medium', 60, 'unsubstantiated', 'This claim requires transparency regarding the baseline year (2020), the scope of the carbon footprint assessment (e.g., Scope 1, 2, and 3 emissions), and the methodology used for calculating the reduction. Without this information, it''s difficult to verify the claim''s accuracy and relevance.', 'Green Claims Code', 'Principle 3: Claims must not omit or hide important information', 'uk', 'Clearly define the scope, methodology, and baseline year used for calculating the carbon footprint reduction. Provide supporting data or a link to a publicly available report.', 'We have reduced our Scope 1 and 2 carbon emissions by 50% since 2020, calculated according to [methodology] and verified by [third-party].', 3, '2026-01-29 15:04:45.819044+00'),
	('6b733cce-a889-436d-8366-95bfc89f4507', 'b231480e-b5dd-4203-b154-6963c50f23e2', 'Our company is committed to being 100% carbon neutral by 2030.', 'Overall company commitment', 'medium', 65, 'future_promise', 'The claim of 100% carbon neutrality by 2030 is a future promise that requires a clear and verifiable plan. It lacks details on how this will be achieved and what methodologies will be used. Without transparency, it could be considered misleading.', 'Green Claims Code (CMA, 2021)', 'Principle 6: Claims must be substantiated', 'uk', 'Provide a detailed plan outlining the steps to achieve carbon neutrality, including specific targets, methodologies, and verification processes.', 'Our company is committed to achieving carbon neutrality by 2030 through [specific actions and methodologies], verified by [third-party certification].', 0, '2026-01-29 15:06:16.384725+00'),
	('1e9836da-a8a8-438d-9d05-3cf1e3384233', 'b231480e-b5dd-4203-b154-6963c50f23e2', 'We use eco-friendly materials in all our products.', 'Materials used in products', 'high', 80, 'vague_claim', 'The term ''eco-friendly'' is vague and lacks specific meaning. It does not provide consumers with enough information to assess the environmental impact of the materials. This violates the requirement for claims to be clear and unambiguous.', 'Directive on Empowering Consumers for the Green Transition (2024/825)', 'Article [Relevant Article]', 'eu', 'Replace ''eco-friendly'' with specific details about the materials'' environmental attributes, such as recycled content, renewable sourcing, or reduced carbon footprint. Provide supporting data or certifications.', 'We use materials with [X]% recycled content, sourced from [sustainable source], which reduces our carbon footprint by [Y]%.', 1, '2026-01-29 15:06:16.384725+00'),
	('3fbcd30d-fbad-4e61-9c1a-d47f2305c407', 'b231480e-b5dd-4203-b154-6963c50f23e2', 'Our packaging is made from recycled materials and is fully biodegradable.', 'Packaging materials', 'medium', 70, 'unsubstantiated', 'The claim that the packaging is ''fully biodegradable'' requires substantiation. It needs to specify the conditions under which biodegradation occurs (e.g., industrial composting) and provide evidence to support the claim, such as certification or testing results. Without this, it could mislead consumers.', 'Green Claims Code (CMA, 2021)', 'Principle 6: Claims must be substantiated', 'uk', 'Specify the conditions required for biodegradation and provide evidence of certification or testing to support the claim. If it only biodegrades in industrial composting facilities, this must be clearly stated.', 'Our packaging is made from [X]% recycled materials and is biodegradable in [specific conditions, e.g., industrial composting facilities] according to [standard/certification].', 2, '2026-01-29 15:06:16.384725+00'),
	('83cdb986-7484-432a-b215-331d12235874', 'b231480e-b5dd-4203-b154-6963c50f23e2', 'We have reduced our carbon footprint by 50% since 2020.', 'Company''s carbon footprint reduction', 'medium', 55, 'unsubstantiated', 'While a positive statement, the claim lacks transparency regarding the baseline, scope, and methodology used to calculate the carbon footprint reduction. Without this information, it''s difficult to verify the claim''s accuracy and could be misleading.', 'Green Claims Code (CMA, 2021)', 'Principle 6: Claims must be substantiated', 'uk', 'Provide details on the baseline year (2020), the scope of the carbon footprint assessment (e.g., Scope 1, 2, and 3 emissions), and the methodology used for calculation. Consider third-party verification.', 'We have reduced our carbon footprint (Scope 1, 2, and 3 emissions) by 50% since 2020, based on [methodology] and verified by [third-party].', 3, '2026-01-29 15:06:16.384725+00');
